{
  "text": "This susceptibility limit is directly set by the inverse length scale q 0 that enters in the specification of the local plasmon dispersion [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] . We compute this susceptibility limit from the electron-density variation n(r) that we have established in the underlying (full) vdW-DF-cx calculations.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "6604518",
    "[CITATION_2]": "29097610",
